with pytest.raises(RuntimeError), expected_protocol(ik.toptica.TopMode, [
    "(param-ref 'laser1:charm:correction-status)",
    "(param-ref 'laser1:charm:reg:started)"], [
    "(param-ref 'laser1:charm:correction-status)", '0',
    "> (param-ref 'laser1:charm:reg:started)", '""', '> '], sep='\r\n') as tm:
    _date = datetime(2012, 12, 1, 1, 2, 1)
    assert tm.laser[0].lock_start == _date
